# NutriAI environment configuration
# Copy this file to `.env` and fill in your keys. NEVER commit `.env`.
#
# The OpenRouter key is server-side ONLY. On Cloudflare Pages it is set as a
# Pages environment variable / secret named OPENROUTER_API_KEY (Dashboard ->
# Settings -> Environment variables, or `wrangler pages secret put`). It is
# never exposed to the browser.
#
# For local Pages Functions testing you may put it in `.env` (loaded by
# `wrangler pages dev`); the frontend build does not read it.

OPENROUTER_API_KEY=
